                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-6-off26 t18220417-6-cd27"></join>, one set of cruets and stands, value 10 s.; one musical box, value 5 l.; four spoons, value 10 s., and one pair of sugar-tongs, value 10 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220417-6-victim97" type="victimName">
